Test for the `dune describe` command
====================================

Setup
-----

  $ cat >dune-project <<EOF
  > (lang dune 2.3)
  > (package (name foo))
  > EOF

  $ cat >dune <<EOF
  > (library
  >  (public_name foo)
  >  (libraries foo.x)
  >  (modules foo))
  > 
  > (library
  >  (name foo_x)
  >  (public_name foo.x)
  >  (modules foo_x))
  > EOF

  $ touch foo.ml
  $ touch foo_x.ml

